data.name: SAFETY SCALP VEIN SETS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% medical grade stainless steel
- Polyethylene (PE) Wings
- Polypropylene (PP) Connector, Cap and Needle Cover
- PVC and DEHP-Free Tubing

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Color-Coded Size Identification
- Male Luer Lock and holder’s Luer Connector + Cap

## PERFORMANCE
- Easy Activation Safety Slide Mechanism
- inviolable closure technology
- 3 bevelled tip sharpness technology
- Soft and anti-slip Surface colored Fixiation Wings
- High Transparency and Memory Tubing
- Air-Tight sealing with syringe’s tip
- Automatic Lubrication’s Technology => Optimal result on penetration resistance
